{"tid":2463117,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[南韓起源]被指歪曲史實、使用中式道具　南韓古裝劇停播","createTime":"2021-03-26T12:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:02:49.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe23b8c65c83beb4b2ba4923f3ac5063271d01c9","tid":2463117,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】南韓有古裝電視劇被指歪曲史實及使用中式道具，要停播。<br />\n耗資320億韓元、即近2.2億港元拍攝的這套古裝韓劇，播出首兩集引起廣泛批評。劇集以朝鮮時代作背景，但出現月餅、皮蛋等中式食物，部分角色亦穿著中式服裝。劇中，朝鮮太宗濫殺百姓的情節被指醜化其形象、歪曲歷史。<br />\n兩日已有逾20萬人在青瓦台網頁聯署，要求停播劇集。加上劇集贊助商全部撤資，電視台和製作公司決定停播這套韓劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/728180?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F728180%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=47e68333\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F728180%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM&h=6e25d2ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/728180?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM</a>"},{"pid":"667706da738b33a83bec5538641be82a937cd605","tid":2463117,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:50:00.000Z","msg":"泡菜國換埋國旗算啦<br />\n使用中式國旗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a471a023f7066e4abfed70ace96f888bc87f00","tid":2463117,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"劇組仆得街,出資咁多錢,比人屌到落架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa